Project Description

Marketplace for managing and distributing programming tasks.

Goals
1. Create a new developer community to outsource programming tasks.
2. Create new job opportunities for programmers and designers.
3. Enable great minds to express themselves, help others and gain a
reputation for their work.
4. Train your programming skills by doing tasks from different aspects
and with an increasing level of difficulty.
5. Create an easy gateway for businesses to hire and contact appropriate
outsource for each task that they need to perform.
